      %section{ :id => 'bio' }
        %p
          I am a front-end web developer living in the New York area. Currently, I am employed as a Senior Open Standards Developer at R/GA, where I 
          enjoy creating rich user-interfaces and experiences with javascript, HTML and CSS.
        %p
          For server-side work, I always lean towards Ruby and either MySQL or MongoDB. I have played around with Node, but I have yet to find 
          a good enough reason to use it for a project.

